                <Paragraphs>
                  <Paragraph>
                    <TextRuns>
                      <TextRun>
                        <Value>1.The broad and specific Directorate/Department/Section priority objectives and targets are derived from and aligned to the Annual Work Plan, Performance Contract and Job Description.</Value>
                        <Style>
                          <FontStyle>Normal</FontStyle>
                          <FontFamily>Arial Narrow</FontFamily>
