                          <Color>#000000</Color>
                        </Style>
                      </TextRun>
                      <TextRun>
                        <Value>These objectives must adhere to the SMARTER rules – i.e. Specific, Measurable, Attainable, Relevant, Timebound, Evaluation and Review.</Value>
                        <Style>
